snippet.title: FRANCE IS UNBEATABLE | A Small World Cup First Impressions
snippet.description:
►Click SHOW MORE for more info!◄ 
A Small World Cup is a free Itch.io game where you have to win against the CPU in a quick mouse-dragging game. It's MUCH harder than it looks I PROMISE.


- ABOUT THE GAME -

A Small World Cup on Itch.io: https://rujogames.itch.io/a-small-world-cup

From the creator: This game was my entry for ludum dare #38 compo theme "A Small World" made in 2 days using Construct2.


If you want more new game content you can check the weekly "LOST ON STEAM" video for more new and unknown Steam games or explore the links below. You can also join the Steam Group below to stay up-to-date on all the game reviews I do. I bet I can find a few that you haven't heard of!


-------------------------------------

► Subscribe for more content everyday: https://goo.gl/zWmCfy ◄ 

►Join the Sonoket Lounge Discord: https://discord.gg/8Ryvx2g

-------------------------------------

Sonoket Gaming is the place where I hope to be able to bring some freakin joy to your lives. If I can make you laugh, cry or feel something you haven't felt before then I'll say that I've done it. I love you.
